{"tid":1538842,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"乜野「階段性勝利」？五大訴求呀！","createTime":"2019-09-04T08:01:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T09:07:15.000Z","uid":222190,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d9bf281827acff2c435f6f6efa8b7ebf240b0e22","tid":1538842,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:01:52.000Z","msg":"全部人呢世記住<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"be9e7a07b121b334e45314a4bf1da8d0f773514f","tid":1538842,"uid":273889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:02:52.000Z","msg":"政府要輸得起<br />\n五件都要跳晒落去<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zqu1J3R.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzqu1J3R.gif&h=bf7c04b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d1055422b2c934d5f7880dbcb398a88a5c818ea","tid":1538842,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:03:06.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97529d143b7890470a8faa1144e9e2d1ad7825f6","tid":1538842,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be9e7a07b121b334e45314a4bf1da8d0f773514f","tid":1538842,"uid":273889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:02:52.000Z","msg":"政府要輸得起<br />\n五件都要跳晒落去<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zqu1J3R.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A